name: hdfeos5
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "5.1.15" %}

package:
    name: hdfeos5
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: HDF-EOS{{ version }}.tar.Z
    url: ftp://edhs1.gsfc.nasa.gov/edhs/hdfeos5/latest_release/HDF-EOS{{ version }}.tar.Z
    sha256: 119588067abf139c1c600a4519b880d04a3933049576c88acdc8ff6fc71803dd
    patches:
        # http://hdfeos.org/forums/showthread.php?t=673
        - EHapi.c.patch

build:
    number: 6
    skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - hdf5 1.8.17|1.8.17.*
        - zlib 1.2.*
    run:
        - hdf5 1.8.17|1.8.17.*
        - zlib 1.2.*

test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libGctp.a  # [unix]
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libhe5_hdfeos.a  # [unix]
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test hdfeos5  # [unix]

about:
    home: http://hdfeos.org/index.php
    license: Public Domain
    summary: 'Earth Observing System HDF.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - jhamman
